These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: juice, cola
Movie-Genre: mystery, thriller
Sport: water-polo, sailing
Transport: airplane, van
1. Transport:van is on the left or right of Sport:sailing##3
2. Beverage:cola is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:thriller == Beverage:juice##1
4. Transport:van is on the right of Transport:airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | juice  | cola   |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller     | mystery   |
| Sport         | sailing | water-polo |
| Transport     | airplane | van    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
Food: zucchini, lemon
Movie-Genre: adventure, horror
Pet: fish, cat
Transport: van, quad-bike
1. Pet:cat is in an odd position##4
2. Movie-Genre:adventure == Transport:quad-bike##1
3. Food:lemon is on the right of Movie-Genre:horror##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | zucchini     | lemon |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | adventure  |
| Pet           | cat         | fish     |
| Transport     | van   | quad-bike    |

 #################################
 
