.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
Job: software-developer, fisherman
Nationality: colombian, japanese
Pet: rabbit, hedgehog
Sport: basketball, parkour
1. Sport:parkour is in an even position##4
2. Nationality:japanese is on the far left or far right##3
3. Job:fisherman == Nationality:colombian##1
4. Pet:rabbit is on the left of Nationality:japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | fisherman | software-developer    |
| Nationality   | colombian       | japanese |
| Pet           | rabbit         | hedgehog    |
| Sport         | basketball    | parkour   |

